{"id":686565,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/686565.html","date":"2022-09-04T13:49:59Z","modified":"2022-09-04T13:49:59Z","title":"【CDTV】武汉市民超市内吐槽高物价：“十五块八一斤的青菜，你要老百姓死哦”","content":"<div style=\"width:100%;margin:0 auto;padding-left:20px\">\n<div class=\"su-spoiler su-spoiler-style-fancy su-spoiler-icon-chevron-circle su-spoiler-closed\" data-scroll-offset=\"0\" data-anchor-in-url=\"no\"><div class=\"su-spoiler-title\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\"><span class=\"su-spoiler-icon\"></span>CDT 档案卡</div><div class=\"su-spoiler-content su-u-clearfix su-u-trim\">\n<strong>标题：</strong>【CDTV】武汉市民超市内吐槽高物价：“十五块八一斤的青菜，你要老百姓死哦”<br />\n<strong>来源：</strong>微博账号@麦小兜妈妈的碎碎念（原作者不详）<br />\n<strong>发表日期：</strong>2022.9.3<br />\n<strong>主题归类：</strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%89%A9%E4%BB%B7\" target=\"_blank\">中国物价</a><br>\n<strong>CDS收藏：</strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E9%A6%86\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">公民馆</a><br>\n<strong>版权说明：</strong>该作品版权归原作者所有。中国数字时代仅对原作进行存档，以对抗中国的网络审查。<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/copyright\">详细版权说明</a>。\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"2022.9.3 武汉市民超市内吐槽高物价：“十五块八一斤的青菜，你要老百姓死哦”\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/gFcjUNarhos?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>9月3日，一则反映中国物价高昂的视频在中文互联网上被传播。</p>\n<p>视频中的画面发生在武汉市某超市内，拍摄视频的市民一边骂着脏话一边吐槽高昂的物价。</p>\n<blockquote><p>\n&#8230;&#8230;白菜十五块八一斤，十五块八一斤的青菜，你要老百姓死哦。娃娃菜十四块八一斤&#8230;&#8230;十二块钱一斤的番茄，十九块钱一斤的洋葱&#8230;&#8230;\n</p></blockquote>\n<p>另一位买菜的市民也对高物价表示不满。</p>\n","author":1092,"categories":[45870,41492,43134,45438,45443,38927],"tags":[10098,10531,42791,45198]}